{"tid":510822,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩佬有火：3億鎊唔夠爭霸","createTime":"2017-12-27T00:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T02:18:24.000Z","uid":28435,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"a755fba2cf0b930baa5789efe8604a74157ebf41","tid":510822,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T00:11:08.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=zJ4NV0q7rwvv%2F7cjtf6SgozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=4fa45d00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯周二英超主場失禮地以2:2逼和般尼，領隊摩連奴再同記者劍拔弩張，並揚言即使有3億鎊也不足爭標。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯一度落後0:2，幸而後備入替的連格大顯神威，梅開二度，扳成2:2平手，避免「拆禮物日」送禮。被記者問到上任後已豪擲3億鎊擴軍，紅魔主帥摩連奴（Jos&eacute; Mourinho）忍不住反擊：「還不夠，曼城有力用收購前鋒的價錢羅致後衛（暗指基爾獲加），要知道，班霸買人的價格往往高於其他球隊，」<br />\n<br />\n「班霸同勁旅是兩回事，我深明班霸意味著甚麼。」每當扯火時，摩佬也會滔滔不絕反駁：「難道你們不認為AC米蘭同曼聯不同層次？難道皇馬遜於曼聯？難道國際米蘭不是班霸？歐洲足球有很多班霸，但未必每一季都有力爭標，悠久歷史造就了班霸的地位。」<br />\n<br />\n「當你們說爭標時，曼聯永遠是當仁不讓，難道熱刺不是嗎？難道阿仙奴沒責任爭標？車路士呢？」摩佬補充道。"},{"pid":"04c99bbd92c08ddfb28ba15e89d724f3a4a04af4","tid":510822,"uid":153,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T00:15:10.000Z","msg":"無利記<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952b85a742efa02ed55f3ad9ead500976780d27c","tid":510822,"uid":97126,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"04c99bbd92c08ddfb28ba15e89d724f3a4a04af4","tid":510822,"uid":153,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T00:15:10.000Z","msg":"無利記<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T00:16:16.000Z","msg":"利記? 邊撚個利記呀 睇過睇過"},{"pid":"22591e1eba2f57130aa096f84aa6b2f65e91609b","tid":510822,"uid":108201,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":